snippet.title: Goetia - Available Now on Steam!
snippet.description:
Goetia is a 2D adventure game taking place in England in the 1940s. Lead Abigail Blackwood, a spectral young girl who died 39 years ago. Explore her childhood manor in search of clues, answers, and traces of her missing family.

​Buy it now:​ http://bit.ly/1TMFWhP

Follow Square Enix Collective: 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/SquareEnixCollective/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/SQEXCollective

Follow Goetia: 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/playgoetia
Twitter: https://twitter.com/playgoetia
